data.description: Just bring your toothbrush!!! Sellers are relocating & reluctantly leaving this absolutely beautiful 5 Bedroom / 3 Full Bath sunny, East-facing home situated on an oversized lot. This spacious home has a wonderful unique floorplan with 2 BRs on the main level - 1 with an en suite bathroom. Newer Roof / AC / Furnace /Washer & Dryer. An expansive living room with a large bow window & cozy fireplace is the perfect spot to spend a leisurely day.  Enjoy holiday gatherings in your formal dining room which is adjacent to an updated kitchen with a large eating area overlooking the beautiful manicured rear yard & paver patio. Centrally located and conveniently located near shopping, parks, and commuter buses & rail
